quran[93]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Ṭaa, Sɩɩn, ad woto yaa Alkʋrãanã Aaya-rãmba, la Gaf sẽn vẽnegde."
  27,2,"ɑ yɑɑ kãndgre la sũ-noogr ne sɩd-kõtba"
  27,3,"Neb nins sẽn yãnesd ne Pʋʋsgã la b kõt zakã la b maan bãng-n-wãak ne Yaoolem Raarã."
  27,4,"La neb nins sẽn ka kõt Yaoolem Raarã sɩdã, Tõnd faasa b tʋʋmã n kõ-bɑ, tɩ b be be n tuumdẽ."
  27,5,"Bãmbã rãmbã tara naon-yooko, la Yaoolem Raarã, bãmb la bõndbã."
  27,6,"Ad fo reegda Alkʋrãanã n yi Bʋʋd-mitã sẽn yɑɑ Bãngdã nengẽ."
  27,7,"Tẽeg wakat ning a Musa sẽn yeel a zakã rãmba: ""ad mam yãnda bugum, tõe tɩ m wa ne kɩbar n kõ-y maa bug-vɩlengɑ tɩ y paam n woode''."
  27,8,"Lɑ a sẽn wa n ta-a wã, b bool-a lɑme, ''bark be ne Soab ning sẽn be bugumẽ la Soab ning sẽn be a kɩrengẽ wã, yɩlgemd be ne Wẽnde sẽn yaa bõn-naandɩ Soaba''."
  27,9,"""Yaa foom a Musa, ad Maam la Wẽnd sẽn yaa wilb Naabã, n yaa Bʋʋd Mitã"""
  27,10,"La ""lobg f rasaarã"". La a sẽn wa n yã-a t'a rãmbd wala waafã, a lebg n na n zoeeme, n ka yals n ges ye. A Musa, ra yaees ye, ad Tẽn-tʋʋmbã ka yaeesd Mam nengẽ ye,"
  27,11,"Rẽnda ned ning sẽn wẽge, rẽ loogr poorẽ t'a tedg sõmblem ɑ wẽngrã poorẽ, rẽnd Mam yaa Yaafg Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  27,12,"Lɑ tʋm f nugã f fuugã loorẽ, t'a na n yiime n yɑɑ pεεlga, lɑ pa bãag ye, yaa tagmas a wae wã a yembr la woto; kẽng a Fɩr-ʿaoon la a nebã nengẽ, bala b yɩɩme n yɑɑ dĩin-yitba."
  27,13,"Wakat ning Tõnd tagmasã sẽn wa b nengẽ, n yaa vẽenese, b yeelame: ""ad woto yaa tɩɩm sẽn vẽnege!"""
  27,14,"La b maan sõm-zɩɩlem ne-a tɩ bãmb mengã yaool n maan bãng-n-wãag ne wẽgd la zẽk-m-menga, bɩ f ges yaa wãn la sãamdbã baasgã yɩ yã."
  27,15,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd kõo a Daawʋʋd la a Sʋlaymaan bãngre, tɩ b yiibã yeele: "" pẽgr be ne Wẽnd sẽn mɑɑnɑ tõnd tɩ d yɩɩd sɩd-kõtb wʋsg sẽn yaa A yembsã""."
  27,16,"T'a Sʋleymaan rɩk a Daawʋʋd faado, n yeele: ""yaa yãmb nebã! b wĩniga tõnd liuuli goam la b kõ tõnd bũmb fãa, la ad woto yaa yɩɩdlem sẽn vẽnege""."
  27,17,"La b tigmɑ me n kõ a Sʋlaymaane, a sodaasã sẽn yɑɑ zĩn-dãmbã lɑ ninsɑɑlbã la luiili wã, n tong-ba"
  27,18,"hal tɩ b kẽn n wa tʋg n ta gũyã kosoogẽ, la gũur sẽn yeele: ""yaa yãmb gũyã! kẽ-y rotẽ wã, t'a Sʋlaymaan la a sodãasã ra wa tab yãmb n ka bãng ye""!"
  27,19,"La a Sʋlaymaan na n yõgem a noorã n laadẽ gũurã koεεgã yĩnga, la a yeele: ""yaa m Soaba! leems maam tɩ m pʋʋs bark ne Fo neemã wã Fo sẽn maan n kõ maamã, la mam roagdb a yiibã, la sẽn na yɩlẽ tɩ m tʋm tʋʋm ning Fo sẽn na yard-ɑ, la F kẽes maam Fo yemb sõmã wã pʋgẽ ne F yolsgã""."
  27,20,"Rẽ poorẽ t'a gẽes liuuli wã sʋka n yeele: ""yaa bõe tɩ mam pa ne we-no-raoogã? Bɩ a ka be?"
  27,21,"M na yõk-a n sɩbg-kεgengɑ maa m koadg-a maa t'a wa ne daliil sẽn yaa vẽenega n kõt-ɑ pɑdengɑ''."
  27,22,"La liuulã sẽn yi bilf bɑlɑ lɑ ɑ sẽn wɑ, n yeel ɑ Sʋlɑymɑɑn: ""m paama bãngr fo sẽn pa tare, m waa fo nengẽ ne kɩbar vẽeneg sẽn yi Sabaa:"
  27,23,"Mam tɩ mik-b lame tɩ yaa pag la b naaba, lɑ B kõ-a-la bũmbã fãa, a tara naam-goeel sẽn yaa kãsenga."
  27,24,"M mika na-poakã la a nebã tɩ b maamd wĩntoogã suguudu, zẽng sẽn ka Wẽnde, t'a Sʋɩtãan faas b tʋʋmã n gɩdg-b n yi so-tɩrgẽ, tɩ b ka tõe n kãndg ye."
  27,25,"Yaa bõe yĩng tɩ b pa na n maan suguud Naab ning sẽn yiisd bõn-bεεl saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã yĩnga, la A leb n mi yãmb sẽn solgdã la y sẽn vẽnegdã?"
  27,26,"Soab ka be rẽnda Yẽnda, A yaa Al-ʿars wagellã Soaba۩."
  27,27,"La a Sʋlaymaan yeele: ""d na n gesame fo sẽn togsã yaa sɩd bɩ f yagda zĩri."
  27,28,"Kẽng ne mam seb-kãngã n tɩ lob b nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ loog n bas-b n gese b na n leoka wãn-wãnɑ?"
  27,29,"La na-poakã yeele: ''yaa yãmb mam nebã! ad b loba sebr sẽn yaa wagell tɩ wa mam nengẽ."
  27,30,"Ad sebrã yii a Sʋlaymaan nengẽ n sɩng : ""ne Wẽnd yʋʋre, sẽn yaa Yols-yaleng Naabã, n yaa tũus-n-yols Naabã,"
  27,31,"Ra wa-y n zẽk y mens mam zug ye, la wa-y mam nengẽ ne sak-n-tũ""."
  27,32,"La na-poakã yeele: ""yaa yãmb mam nebã! sagl-y maam m yellã zugu, ad mam pa yɩ n na n kao yell bʋʋdo, rẽndame tɩ y maan kaset ɑ pʋgẽ""."
  27,33,"La b yeele: "" ad tõnd yaa pãens rãmba la zab-kεgens rãmba, bɩ f ges fo sẽn na n sagl bũmb ning bɑlɑ (tɩ tõnd tõe n mɑɑn-ɑ lɑme)""."
  27,34,"La a yeele: ""ad nanɑmbsã sã n kẽ tẽngẽ, b sãamd-a lame la b kɩt tɩ tẽngã nin-zɩsdã lebg nin-yaalse, la yaa woto la b maanda."
  27,35,"Lɑ mam na n tʋma kũun n tɩ kõ-ba, rẽ poorẽ m na n kollame n ges yaa bõe la tʋm-tʋʋmbã na n lebg ne?""."
  27,36,"La wakat ning tʋm-tʋʋmbã sẽn wa a Sʋlaymaan nengẽ, la a yeele: ""yãmb paasda maam arzεka n dɑt tɩ m bɑs-yã?, la ad Wẽnd sẽn kõ maamã sõmblem yɩɩda A sẽn kõ yãmbã, ka woto ye, yãmb kɩdemda ne y kũunã (t'a yaool n ka baa fʋɩ ye)''."
  27,37,"Lebg n kẽng b nengẽ, ad tõnd na n waa b nengẽ ne sodaas b sẽn ka tar tõog ne-ba, la ad tõnd na n yiis-b lɑ beenẽ tɩ b yaa sẽn faag ne paoogre""."
  27,38,"La a Sʋlaymaan yeele: ""yaa yãmb mam neba, ãnd n na n wa ne a naamã goeelã taoor tɩ b nan ka wa mam nengẽ n sak-n-tũ?"""
  27,39,"La zĩn tõtr yeelyã: ""mam tõe n waa ne-a, taoor tɩ fo nan ka yik f zĩigẽ wã ye, ad mam tara pãng ne yel-kãngã n yaa bas-m-yam soaba""."
  27,40,"La ned ning sẽn tar Gafã bãngrã yeele: ""mam na n waa ne-a, taoor tɩ fo nifã ka kams n lebg ye. Rẽnd wakat ning a Sʋlaymaan sẽn wa n yã naamã goeelã t'a rɩg a taoorã, a yeelame: ""ad woto yaa mam Soabã neema, t'A tʋll n rat n zarb maam n ges m na n pʋʋsa bark bɩ, bɩ m na n maana sõm-zɩɩlem. Lɑ ned ning sẽn wa n pʋʋs barka, yaa a meng yĩnga, la ned ning sẽn wa n maan sõm-zɩɩlem, ad mam Soabã yaa sek-m-meng-Soab n yaa wagalle""."
  27,41,"La a Sʋlaymaan yeele: ""tee-y me a naamã goeelã tɩ d gese a na n bãng-a lame bɩ a ka na n bãnge""."
  27,42,"La na-poakã sẽn wa n wa wã, la b yeel-a: ""yaa woto la fo naamã goeele?"" la a yeele: ""ad yaa wala yẽnda"". –[la a Sʋlaymaan yeele]: b reng n kõo tõnd bãngr ne Wẽnd tõogã tɑoor tɩ pagã pɑ miẽ ye, la tõnd rag n yaa sak-n-tũ-rãmba."
  27,43,"Tɩ bũmb ning na-poakã sẽn ra yɩ n tũudẽ wã gɩdg-a lame (t'a ka tõe n yɩ sɩd-kõat ye), bala a rag n yaa sõm-zɩta."
  27,44,"La b yeel-a: ""kẽ gãsgã"". La a sẽn wa n yã-a wã, a sãmbame tɩ yaa koom sẽn zulmi t'a kool n bɑs a kars a yiibã yɩnga, la a [Sʋlaymaan] yeele: ad yaa gãsg sẽn maan ne nin-gets, la na-poakã yeele: ""ad mam rag n wẽga m menga, la moasã m maga a Sʋlaymaan n na n sak n tũ Wẽnd sẽn yaa bõn-naands Soabã."
  27,45,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd tʋmsame tɩ kẽng a Ṯamuud rãmb nengẽ, b saam-biig a Ṣaalɩh [t'a yeel-ba] ""tũ-y Wẽnde"". La b welga taab zãma a yiibu n maan tak-n-taare."
  27,46,"A yeele: ""yaa yãmb mam nebã! yaa bõe yĩng tɩ yãmb yãgd ne yel-wẽnde, n yaool n ka yãgd ne yel-sõmde? Y ka na n kos Wẽnd yaafa tɩ raar ninga b na yols-yã?"
  27,47,"La b yeele: ""Ad yaa foom la neb nins sẽn lagem foomã zu-beedã n be ne tõndo"". La a [Ṣaalɩh] yaale: ""ad yãmb zu-beedã bee Wẽnd nengẽ, yãmb pʋs n yaa neb b sẽn zɑrbd-b ne kõon-dãmbɑ n nɑ n gese''."
  27,48,"La rag n bee tẽngẽ wã, raop a wae sulli, n sãamd tẽngã pʋga, la b pa manegd ye."
  27,49,"B yeelame: ""d wẽen ne Wẽnd tɩ tõnd na n kʋ-a lame ne a zakã rãmba yʋng wɑkɑto, la d yeel a nedã: ""tõnd pa tar kaset ne yẽ la a zakã rãmb kʋʋbã ye, la tõnd yaa sɩd-rãmba""."
  27,50,"La b rabs b rabrã tɩ Tõnd na n lebs b rabrã tɩ b ka miẽ ye."
  27,51,"Bɩ f ges b rabrã baasg yɩɩ wãnã? Tõnd halk-b lame la b nebã fãa gilli."
  27,52,"Ad woto yaa b rotã lebgɑ rɑboodo n yɑɑ vɩɩdo b sẽn wẽg b mensã yĩnga, ad tɑgmɑs bee woto pʋgẽ ne neb sẽn tagsd n getẽ wã."
  27,53,"La Tõnd na n tɩlg neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã la b yɩ n zoet Wẽndã."
  27,54,"La [tẽeg] a Lʋʋṭ yelle, a sẽn wa n yeel a nebã, rẽ yĩnga yãmb wata ne yel-beedo, tɩ yãmb mensã ne tɑɑbɑ?"
  27,55,"Ad yãmb wata rap nengẽ ne yɑmleoogo lɑ wʋm-noog (baoobo) zẽng sẽn pa pagba, ad yãmb yaa zɩtb zãma."
  27,56,"A nebã leokr pa yɩ, rẽnda b sẽn yeele: ""yiis-y a Lʋʋṭ zakã rãmb y tẽngã pʋgẽ, ad b yaa neb sẽn yɑɑ yɩlg-m-meng rãmb n yi rẽgdo."
  27,57,"Tɩ Tõnd na n tɩlg-a la a zakã rãmba, rẽnda a pagã. Ad Tõnd bʋʋm t'a na n pɑɑ hɑlkdbã pʋgẽ."
  27,58,"La Tõnd niis b zug kug sɑɑgɑ, rẽnd bugs-n-kong rãmb saag yɩ wẽnga."
  27,59,"Yeele : ""pẽgr be ne Wẽnde, la tɩlgr lɑ bɑs-m-yɑm be ne A yembs nins A sẽn tũusã (Nɑbiyɑɑmã sɑhɑɑbsã), rẽ yĩnga yaa Wẽnd n yɩɩd sõmblem bɩ yaa bũmb ning bãmb sẽn maan lagem-n-taarã?"
  27,60,"Bɩ yaa Naab Ning sẽn naan saasã la tẽngã la A sik saasẽ wã sa-koom t'a kɩt tɩ pʋt bul n tob tɩ be neere, yãmb ra pa tõe n buls a tɩɩsã dɛ. Rẽ yĩnga soab zẽng n be ne Wẽnde? Pa woto ye, ad bãmb yaa neb sẽn golemd n baood lagem-n-taas n mɑkd ne Wẽnde."
  27,61,"Bɩ yaa Naab ning sẽn maan-a tẽngã tɩ yaa tablg zĩigã la A maan ko-sood a pʋgẽ, la A ning tãms a zugu, la A maan mog a yiibã ne taab sʋk gɩdre. Rẽ yĩnga soab zẽng n be n lɑgem Wẽnde? Ka woto ye, ad b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  27,62,"Bɩ yɑɑ sẽn reegd-ɑ keelem soab kosgã t'a sã n bool-A la A zẽkd wẽngã, lɑ A maan yãmb tɩ y yɑɑ ledsdb n ledsd taab tẽn-gãngã zugu. Rẽ yĩnga soab zẽng n be ne Wẽnde? Ad pɑood yãmb sẽn tẽegd n tɑgsdẽ."
  27,63,"Bɩ yaa sẽn peegd-ɑ yãmb wen-vɩʋʋgã ligsẽ la mogrã ligsẽ wã, la A tʋmsd sebgã tɩ yaa sũ-noogr n lʋɩɩsd A yolsgã tɑoore (sa-koomã). Rẽ yĩnga soab zẽng n be n lɑgm Wẽnde? Wẽnd naamã zẽkame n yi bũmb ning bãmb sẽn maand lagem-n-taarã."
  27,64,"Bɩ yɑɑ sẽn yẽbgd-ɑ naanegã, rẽ poorẽ t'A lebg n vʋʋg-ɑ, la A rɩlgd yãmb ne rɩtl sẽn yi saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã. Rẽ yĩnga soab zẽng n be ne Wẽnde? Yeele: ""wa-y ne y daliilã tɩ y sã n yɩɩme n yaa sɩd-rãmba''."
  27,65,"Yeele: ""bõn-naands nins sẽn be saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã pa mi sẽn lill ye, rẽnda Wẽnd A ye; ad b ka mi wakat ning b sẽn na n wa yik-b me ye."
  27,66,"Ka woto ye, bɩ b bãngrã pʋgɑ tɑɑbɑ sẽn kẽed yaoolem raarã yεlẽ tɩ b tɑr bãng-n-wãɑkɑ ne-ɑ? Pɑ boto ye, b pʋs n bee sik lɑ yirbg pʋgẽ; ɑee, bãmb pʋs n bee zondlem pʋgẽ sẽn kẽed ne yel-kãnga."
  27,67,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn kɩflã yeelame: "" Rẽ yĩnga tõnd la d saam-rãmbã sã n ki n lebg tom, b na n leb n yiisa tõnd vɩɩse?"
  27,68,"Ad b pʋlem-d-lɑ wãnde tõnd ne d saam-dãmbã sẽn reng taoore, woto pa yɩ rẽndame tɩ yɑɑ rãeenem rãmbã zĩrimbeedo."
  27,69,"Yeele: ""kẽn-y tẽn-gãngã zugu n tɑgs n ges nin-wẽnsã baasg yɩɩ wãn-wãnɑ?"""
  27,70,"Ra wa sãam f sũur b tõdgrã poorẽ ye, la ra wa weoog f yãoogã ne bũmb ning b sẽn rabsdã ye."
  27,71,"La b yetɑme: ""yaa rabʋr la pʋlen-kãngã nɑ n yɩ, tɩ yãmb sã n yɑɑ sɩda-rãmbɑ?"""
  27,72,"Yeele: ""tõe tɩ pẽnegɑ yãmb y sẽn yãgd ne wã sãndɑ sẽn yɑɑ sɩbgrã''."
  27,73,"Lɑ ɑd fo Soabã yaa yɩɩdlem kõtɑ ne nebã, la ad b wʋsgã fãa ka pʋʋsd bark ye."
  27,74,"La ad fo Soabã mii bũmb ning b sẽn solgd b sũyẽ wã la bũmb ning b sẽn vẽnegdã."
  27,75,"La bũmb ka be n lill ne nebã saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã, rẽndame t'a gʋlsɑme tɩ be Gɑf sẽn yaa vẽeneg pʋgẽ."
  27,76,"Ad Alkʋrãan-kãngã togsda ɭsrayεl koambã yelle, bũmb nins bãmb sẽn wʋsgd ne yõs-taab a zugã fãɑ n vẽnegd b kedgrã."
  27,77,"La ad a yaa kãndgr la yolsg n kõ sɩd-kõtbã."
  27,78,"Ad fo Soabã, A na n bʋʋ b sʋka, la Yẽnda la wilb Naab n yaa minim Naaba."
  27,79,"Bɩ f bobl f meng ne Wẽnde, ɑd fo bee sɩd sẽn yaa vẽeneg zugu"
  27,80,"Fo ka tõe n wʋms kũ-rãmb ye, (sũy sẽn ki rãmbã b kɩfɩlmã yĩngɑ); fo le ka tõe n wʋms wʋng ne f boaala, tɩ b sã n gũd b zãn-kuds n bɑlld n bɑsd foom ye."
  27,81,"Lɑ ɑd fo ka tõe n kãndg zoees n yi b menengã pʋg ye, fo sẽn tõe n wʋms yaa neb nins sẽn kõt sɩd ne Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã tɩ b yaa sak-n-tũ-rãmbã."
  27,82,"La sɩbgrã sã n na n wa sik b zug n sɑ, Tõnd yiisda rũng tẽngã zugu( yɑɑ dũni yikrã tɑgmɑs-rãmbã yembre), t'a gom ne-b b sẽn wʋmde: ""tɩ ɑd nebã rag n dɑ yɩɩme n pa kõt sɩd ne Tõnd tagmas-rãmbɑ ye''."
  27,83,"Lɑ tẽeg raar ning Tõnd sẽn na n wa tigim zãma fãa sulli, sẽn yɑɑ neb nins sẽn yɑgsd tõnd Aɑyɑ-rãmbã tɩ bãmb yɑɑ sẽn tigim tɑɑb tɩ b kãɑgd-bɑ."
  27,84,"Hal tɩ b sã n wa tɩ ta, [Wẽnd] yetdame: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb sak n yagsa Mam Aaya-rãmbã, tɩ yãmb minmã yaool n ka gũbg ne-ba? Bɩ yaa bõe la yãmb rag n maanda?"""
  27,85,"Tɩ Wẽnd sɩbgrã lʋɩ b zugu, b sẽn wẽg b mensã yĩngã, tɩ b pa tar koεεg n na n yeel ye."
  27,86,"Rẽ yĩnga b pa yã tɩ Wẽnd naana yʋngã tɩ b vʋʋs a pʋgẽ la wĩntoogã tɩ yaa vẽenega, ad bee woto pʋga tagmas ne neb sẽn kõt sɩda."
  27,87,"La raar ning b sẽn na n fʋʋs baorgẽ wã, tɩ bũmb ning sẽn be saasẽ wã la sẽn be tẽngẽ wã na n yaeese. Rẽnda neb nins Wẽnd sẽn tʋlle, b fãa na n waa A nengẽ ne sik-m-menga."
  27,88,"Tɩ fo yã tãemsã tɩ yaa wala b kʋɩ n yãsame, tɩ b yaool zoet wala sawato, yaa Wẽnd naanego A sẽn maneg bũmbã fãa naanegã, ad A yaa Minim Tẽng-n-biig ne b sẽn maand bũmb ningã."
  27,89,"Ned ning sẽn wa-a ne yel-sõmde, a tara yel-sõmd sẽn yɩɩd rẽnda, la ra-kãng raare b paamda bas-m-yam n yi raarã wẽnga."
  27,90,"La neb nins sẽn wa-b ne tʋʋm wẽnde, b na n fũgna b nemsã bugmẽ wã. Rẽ yĩnga b na n rola bãmb bõn-zẽng tɩ pa b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã la?"""
  27,91,"Ad b sagla maam tɩ m tũ tẽn-kãngã Soabã, Naab ning sẽn maan-a t'a yaa laohorem tẽngã, n yaa Naab ning sẽn so bũmb fãa wã. La b sagla maam tɩ m yɩ sak-n-tũ soaba."
  27,92,"(la b sagla maam) tɩ m karem Alkʋrãanã, la ned ning sẽn kãndg-a, a kãndgr bee ne a menga, la ned ning sẽn menem-a bɩ f yeele: ""ad mam yaa bugsd bala""."
  27,93,"La yeele: ""pẽgr be ne Wẽnde'', A na n wĩniga yãmb A yel-soalmã, tɩ y bãng-ba, la fo Soabã ka na n maan yam yaal-yaal ne b sẽn tʋmdã ye ( A ka na bas bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmdã n ka rol-b ye)."
